ke":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:40:21.000Z","msg":"撐達個班呢"},{"pid":"d2fb2e3f584ff6237153d0530ee3bd7306573eea","tid":1550005,"uid":212336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1bd5c5cc0b96805a40c172b0a01032245fef201b","tid":1550005,"uid":38523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:40:21.000Z","msg":"撐達個班呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:41:30.000Z","msg":"縮返入閪到"},{"pid":"dd70beed6d333eec6a995ac33961203bc6dd9ac8","tid":1550005,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b42ab6a3c6fb30e1111099bfcdeea1c5aaa47c","tid":1550005,"uid":54574,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1bd5c5cc0b96805a40c172b0a01032245fef201b","tid":1550005,"uid":38523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:40:21.000Z","msg":"撐達個班呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:10:13.000Z","msg":"去哂大灣區"},{"pid":"30d6ae901e48db8f4fc280ffe856bb9911a9686c","tid":1550005,"uid":279145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:12:14.000Z","msg":"共狗"},{"pid":"880e853733459f5c1744fd0ca3d1a520e5b0dccf","tid":1550005,"uid":100831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"個會紅到仆街，會長楊全盛2016年同莫乃光爭立法會IT界個位。<br />\n<br />\n當年種票，ICAC早幾日先告咗十幾個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//廉政公署2017年拘捕72人，涉於2016年立法會資訊科技界選舉種票，事隔逾兩年，終起訴17人，包括7名的士司機從業員總會（的總）理事會成員、職員及會員，涉嫌賄選及種票，當中4人涉以240人的虛假專業資格及學歷，申請為電機暨電子工程師學會（IEEE）香港分會成員，藉此登記為資訊科技界選民，以投票予特定候選人。其餘被告包括的總涉案者的親友，分別有學生、家庭主婦、收銀員、髮型屋助理，部分人涉以金錢引誘他人投票予某候選人，亦有人收取700至1000元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190906/s00002/1567708055177/%E6%B6%89it%E7%95%8C%E8%B3%84%E9%81%B8%E7%A8%AE%E7%A5%A8-%E7%9A%84%E7%B8%BD7%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7-%E8%99%9B%E5%A0%B1240%E4%BA%BA%E5%AD%B8%E6%AD%B7%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5ieee-%E8%A6%AA%E5%8F%8B%E6%9